#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Course Blocks Settings"
msgstr "課程模組設定"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Enable or disable which blocks are visible in the course lesson editor."
msgstr "啟用或停用課程編輯器中顯示的模組。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Available Blocks"
msgstr "可用區塊"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "儲存設定"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid ""
"Customize the appearance and layout of course lessons and the lesson editor. "
"Each setting works independently."
msgstr "自訂課程課件和課件編輯器的外觀和佈局。每項設定均可獨立生效。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Lesson Page Settings"
msgstr "課程頁面設定"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Enhanced Lesson Page Styling"
msgstr "增強課程頁面樣式"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid ""
"Apply enhanced styling to the lesson viewer including improved header, "
"sidebar appearance, content layout, and visual refinements."
msgstr ""
"對課程檢視器套用增強樣式，包括改進標題、側邊欄外觀、內容版面和視覺優化。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Move Sidebar to Left"
msgstr "將側邊欄移至左側"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid ""
"Position the lessons list sidebar on the left side instead of the default "
"right side."
msgstr "將課程清單側邊欄放置在左側，而不是預設的右側。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Custom Content Width"
msgstr "自訂內容寬度"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Override the default lesson content width with a custom value."
msgstr "使用自訂值覆寫預設的課程內容寬度。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Content Width"
msgstr "內容寬度"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Set the maximum width for lesson content. Default is 720px."
msgstr "設定課程內容的最大寬度。預設值為 720 像素。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "px"
msgstr "像素"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Lesson Editor Settings"
msgstr "課程編輯器設定"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Editor Sidebar Enhancement"
msgstr "編輯器側邊欄增強"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid ""
"Add interactive controls to the lesson editor sidebar for better workspace "
"management."
msgstr "在課程編輯器側邊欄新增互動式控件，以便更好地管理工作區。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Off"
msgstr "離開"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Use the default Fluent Community editor sidebar without modifications."
msgstr "使用 Fluent Community 編輯器預設的側邊欄，無需修改。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Collapsible"
msgstr "可折疊的"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Add a toggle button to collapse and expand the sidebar."
msgstr "新增一個切換按鈕，用於折疊和展開側邊欄。"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Resizable"
msgstr "可調整大小"

#: includes/class-course-blocks-admin.php
msgid "Add a drag handle to resize the sidebar width."
msgstr "新增拖曳手把以調整側邊欄寬度。"

